## Healthcheck

```dockerfile
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=5s --start-period=15s --retries=3 \
    CMD wget -qO- http://localhost:3001/health || exit 1
```

Le backend attend que ce healthcheck passe avant de démarrer (`depends_on: condition: service_healthy`).

---

## Build et lancement

```bash
# Build seul
DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1 docker compose build service_data

# Lancement
docker compose up -d service_data

# Logs (cycles de collecte visibles)
docker compose logs -f service_data
```
